<FONT size=1>Yesterday i worked ...5-9. me and manda jetted outta work to go buy her shoes..haha :D then we went to wendys and ate inside and randys manager was being stupid. w.e. so then i came home and i saw someones truck in front of the house. i cant beliee him. fuckin stalker!! who does that? seriously fuckin leave us alone asshole! hmm i work today at 1030 until close. im gonna try and get my department done early cause janice is closing and i need to leave early. i have 2 major tests monday and i didnt study...should i study? do i ever study? i really dont want to fail psychology tho. randy told me to cheat but i feel so guilty sometimes. i have tommorrow off!!! yess!.  i have to read a book..i have like 200 pages left for summer reading that is due thursday. im dead. last driving lesson tuesday . joy   randy better wake up to bring me to work...i called him at 9 like he said and he didnt pick up! >< well i gotta go.later</FONT>
